snippet: Jonas Blixt, who was sidelined for two months because of a rib injury, birdied three of his last four holes to tie Brendon de Jonge in the second round of the Las Vegas Open.
abstract: Jonas Blixt, Ryan Moore and Brendon de Jonge share third-round lead at the Las Vegas Open; other golf results noted.
lead_paragraph: Jonas Blixt, who was sidelined for two months because of a rib injury, birdied three of his last four holes to tie Brendon de Jonge in the second round of the Las Vegas Open.

headline.seo: Brendon De Jonge and Jonas Blixt Share Lead in Las Vegas
headline.main: De Jonge and Blixt Share Lead in Las Vegas
